{
  "title": "Fatty Bouncy Ethiopian Samphire Azifa",
  "description": "A crowd-pleasing Ethiopian dish featuring samphire, this fatty and bouncy azifa is a stir-fry made with tender samphire and a blend of spices, perfect for a quick and delicious meal.",
  "cuisine": "Ethiopian",
